      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is very important that you do not stop taking your antibiotics just because you feel better. Stopping early can allow the infection to return, often stronger than before, because some bacteria may not have been fully killed. Please continue taking the medication exactly as prescribed for the full duration specified by your doctor. If you have any concerns about the course of treatment, contact your healthcare provider immediately.",
